== 製作 ==
2018年10月，宣佈[[喬治·米勒|喬治·米勒]]下一部作品片名為《三千年的渴望》（{{lang|en|''Three Thousand Years of Longing''}}），並預計於2019年開始拍攝<ref>{{Cite web|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|url=https://deadline.com/2018/10/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-three-thousand-years-longing-afm-1202488950/|title=AFM Hot Pic: George Miller To Direct Movie Epic ‘Three Thousand Years Of Longing’, FilmNation To Launch Sales|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2018-10-24|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2018-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025031903/https://deadline.com/2018/10/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-three-thousand-years-longing-afm-1202488950/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，宣佈[[伊卓瑞斯·艾巴|伊卓瑞斯·艾巴]]和[[蒂妲·絲雲頓|蒂妲·絲雲頓]]加盟主演陣容<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/idris-elba-tilda-swinton-star-george-millers-epic-1154996|title=Idris Elba, Tilda Swinton to Star in George Miller's Epic Love Story 'Three Thousand Years of Longing' (Exclusive)|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2018-10-25|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2018-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025211052/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/idris-elba-tilda-swinton-star-george-millers-epic-1154996|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年7月，米勒表示前期製作將於2019年年末開始進行，並預計於2020年3月在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]開始拍攝<ref>{{Cite web|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-sequel-superhero-movie-debate-start-date-three-thousand-years-of-longing-interview-1202802441/|title=George Miller On March Start Date For Next Film, More ‘Mad Max’, Defending Superheroes As Cinema & The Search For Depth That Makes Movies Like ‘Fury Road’ Unforgettable|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-12-06|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206191749/https://deadline.com/2019/12/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-sequel-superhero-movie-debate-start-date-three-thousand-years-of-longing-interview-1202802441/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而受[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]影響，拍攝工作延期至2020年11月在澳大利亞開始進行<ref>{{Cite web|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/george-miller-three-thousand-years-longing-tilda-swinton-idris-elba-underway-australia-john-seale-1234652944/|title=George Miller’s ‘Three Thousand Years Of Longing’ Underway In Australia; Oscar-Winning DoP John Seale Among ‘Mad Max: Fury Road’ Team Re-Uniting On Movie|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-12-09|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209193515/https://deadline.com/2020/12/george-miller-three-thousand-years-longing-tilda-swinton-idris-elba-underway-australia-john-seale-1234652944/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Gemmill|first=Allie|url=https://collider.com/george-miller-new-movie-filming-three-thousand-years-of-longing-idris-elba/|title=George Miller's New Movie 'Three Thousand Years of Longing' Has Already Started Filming|publisher=[[Collider|Collider]]|date=2018-10-24|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2022-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220315150028/https://collider.com/george-miller-new-movie-filming-three-thousand-years-of-longing-idris-elba/}}</ref>。

